  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Effect, tolerance and safety of a supplementation with a probiotic on the risk of
      gastrointestinal infections, on growth, and on gut microbiota in healthy newborn term infants
      born by Cesarean section. Exploratory comparison between a probiotic vs. placebo in the
      formula-fed and in the breastfed feeding groups.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
